\c 112
\s Kuropafadzwa kwomunhu anoda Jehovha
\p
\v 1 Hareruya! Akaropafadzwa munhu anotya Jehovha, Anofarira zvikuru mirairo yake.
\v 2 Vana vake vachava nesimba pasi; Rudzi rwowakarurama rucharopafadzwa.
\v 3 Pfuma ikelvaka~da	mumba make; Kururama kwake kunogara nokusingaperi.
\v 4 Akarurama anobudirwa nechiedza parima;
\ Iye anenyasha, netsitsi nokururama.
\p
\v 5 Ane mufaro munhu uyo anoita nenyasha, anopa chikwerete, Acharuramisirwa mhaka yake
\s pakutonga.
\p
\v 6 Nokuti haangatongozununguswi; Akarurama acharamba achirangarirwa nokusingaperi.
\p
\v 7 Haangatyi mashoko ezvinhu zvakaipa;
\s Mwoyo wake wakasimba,
\s uchavimba naJehovha.
\p
\v 8 Mwoyo wake wakasimbiswa, haangatyi,
\s Kusvikira aona kukundwa kwavadzivisi vake.
\p
\v 9 Akaparadzira, akapa vashaiwi; Kururama kwake kunogara nokusingaperi;
\s Runyanga rwake ruchakwiridzwa nokukudzwa.
\s io Akaipa achazviona, ndokufa neshungu;
\s Achageda-geda meno ake, ndokunyauka;
\s Kuda kwowakaipa kuchaparara.
